# Local scratch notes — do not commit

## configure_cache local variable rename (dspy/clients/__init__.py:37)

The feature branch (feature/apple-foundation-models) renamed the local variable
inside `configure_cache` from `DSPY_CACHE` to `dspy_cache` to suppress the
"shadows outer scope" lint warning. This is a valid cleanup but unrelated to
the Apple feature. Do as a separate commit on main (or a dedicated cleanup PR)
once the feature branch is merged.
